        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This harness of *+1 resilient half plate* is made from the shell plates of a dragon turtle and has the aquadynamic trait. To those who can craft with them, the dense organic plates on the dragon turtle\u2019s body are as valuable as the creature\u2019s hoard of gold.",
